headline: Product Innovation & Global Push Drive Robinhood: Time to Buy HOOD?
summary: Robinhood's innovation blitz, from AI tools to tokenized assets and global expansion, is fueling its meteoric rise and investor optimism. Should you buy?

headline: Should You Reassess Schwab After Its 27.9% Rally in 2025?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Charles Schwab stock right now? You’re not alone. If the performance chart has caught your eye lately, you’ve probably noticed that despite a couple of short-term dips, Schwab’s stock is still reflecting a hefty gain over the longer term. After all, with a 27.9% climb so far this year and a 32.7% jump over the past twelve months, this is a company that’s been nicely rewarding patient investors, even if the past month was a little soft at -1.1%.
